<br>
Picture this:<br>
<br>
2 Guilds, dark and light wish to battle it out, old score to settle, or just for fun... <br>
<br>
Take 2 groups of 16 relatively equal leveled people.. Each group would have:<br>
<br>
8 Tank Classes.<br>
2 Necros<br>
2 Druids<br>
2 Mages<br>
1 Wizard<br>
1 &quot;King&quot; &lt;== Anything, he does nothing.<br>
<br>
Levels would have to be within 3 of each other.<br>
<br>
Everyone stands off against each other in a chess board fasion.  The Kings or guild leaders (what ever) call the moves like you would in Chess.<br>
<br>
The tiwst here is, that when an attack is possible (say a pawn is in diaganol) the 2 parties Dual.. The looser is removed from the &quot;Board&quot; and the winner remains as play piece.  <br>
<br>
No buffing would be allowed in any form.. Just offensive skills, and strategy on the part of the kings.<br>
<br>
Anyhew... Just a thought...<br>
<br>
Night all<br>
